{"tid":1485624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問「留守」如何「不和理非」？","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T18:27:33.000Z","uid":89160,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e09049e6f2c3672cba7439d9c793507b9cf93263","tid":1485624,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>頭盔：我唔會主張今日留守</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n但有太多人係到講「今日係全和理非，你地快d走」，咁我真係想問「留守」點樣「不和理非」法？如果，「留守」係招至「警察暴力」，咁前線就係「不和理非」？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我作為一個和理非，我真係睇唔出留守有乜野暴力成份。</ins></strong><br />\n你話留守班人策略錯，我冇意見，你話人地騎劫你？話人係鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9a9aede434a37140b2a15b4c4df7e4e008d587","tid":1485624,"uid":96460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"[等你返屋企]屋企要人 自貼枕頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">返歸洗腳啦！等佢哋知道幾多人喺屋企等佢哋！唔好浪費170萬人心血</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無黑警無暴力，自動散</span>"},{"pid":"eac34434bc275a6d62085f219e69005f198d37e9","tid":1485624,"uid":89160,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"如果，「留守」係招至「警察暴力」，咁前線就係「不和理非」？<br />\nBlame the victim？"},{"pid":"e42a59de9f7e6a6a1f9d2a4e3b135e83ce9f44c0","tid":1485624,"uid":89160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"和理非到底知唔知乜係非暴力抗爭？係咪搞錯左d野？"},{"pid":"543aec5dd9ddeac0472be6cbc78667a01aaace8c","tid":1485624,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"請問「留守」如何「不和理非」？"},{"pid":"3819ee1cf586a3749acb98d6e722bebf10df0109","tid":1485624,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"請問「留守」如何「不和理非」？和理非出黎答下"},{"pid":"25f96fc1df7569db877a62243cb7411f7407da41","tid":1485624,"uid":89160,"like"